Features :
	- Select a subgrid using mouse events (mousedown, mousemove, mouseup). A subgrid will be created with specified starting and ending coordinates, and it should not overlap any other subgrid.  
	- The subgrid to be moved around the large grid, saving its dimensions, color, and values.
	- The user can copy a selected subgrid and paste it at another position within the large grid.
	- Save the grid state (positions of subgrids) and load it back when needed.


How to run:
	open the "index.html" in browser.
